Coach Issue 11 - 2014  AU

132 Pages | True PDF | English | 17 MB 


Following the success of Australian Men's Health, Coach is the new single subject resource for the ambitious, active man. Presented in an entertaining, informative question-and-answer format, Coach covers such diverse subjects as muscle, weight loss, cardio fitness and nutrition. As the tagline says, Coach is Personal Training for Men
